╠Peter & Muriel Kenny
We wrote your name In the sand, but the waves washed it away
We wrote your name in the sky, but the clouds blew it away
So we wrote your name in our hearts and forever it will stay"█
žIn loving memory of my mum & friend
EILEEN JANE LING 3. 7. 1945 ~ 19.10. 2008
and her special mum, my nanny
DORIS JEAN WEATHERILL 18. 8. 1913 13. 1. 1996
You will both always be in my heart.
In loving memory of my sister and best friend
JULIE CHRISTINA LING
23
15. 10. 68 ~ 18. 5. 10.
you will always be with me and forever in my heart"Ń
